OL,5, Imagine being in court and seeing your 
OL,6, son - a government critic - sentenced  
OL,7, to 25 years in prison.                 
OL,9,FElena Gordon knows exactly how that    
OL,10,Ffeels.                                 
OL,12,FLast month Elena stood beside the dock 
OL,13,F- a glass cage - in a Moscow courtroom.
OL,14,FLocked inside it was her son Vladimir  
OL,15,FKara-Murza.                            
OL,17,FOne of President Putin's most vocal    
OL,18,Fcritics, he was convicted of treason   
OL,19,Fand other alleged crimes and jailed for
OL,20,Fa quarter of a century.                
